# gdalcubes_version

Query gdalcubes version information



```{r include=FALSE}
library(gdalcubes)
```

## Description

Query gdalcubes version information


## Usage


```r
gdalcubes_version()

```


## Value

List with gdalcubes library version information


## Examples


```{r}
gdalcubes_version()
```
